spec_data.Name: texlive-syntrace
spec_data.Description:
This package adds support for traces in trees created using
either the synttree or the qtree package. The package provides
two commands (\traceLabel and \traceReference) to set and use a
trace.
spec_data.Signature: RSA/SHA256, Sun 06 Aug 2017 08:17:55 AM EDT, Key ID f55e7430f5282ee4
spec_data.Summary: Labels for tracing in a syntax tree
